{"title":"【NOIP2014】解方程","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":128,"url":"http://uoj.ac/problem/20","statement":[{"title":"# 题目描述","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<p>已知多项式方程：</p>\n<p>$$a_0+a_1x+a_2x^2+...+a_nx^n=0$$</p>\n<p>求这个方程在$[1,m]$内的整数解（$n$和$m$均为正整数）。</p>\n"},{"title":"# 输入格式","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n\n<p>第一行包含$2$个整数$n$、$m$，每两个整数之间用一个空格隔开。</p>\n<p>接下来的$n+1$行每行包含一个整数，依次为$a_0,a_1,a_2,...,a_n$。</p>\n"},{"title":"# 输出格式","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n\n<p>第一行输出方程在$[1,m]$内的整数解的个数。</p>\n<p>接下来每行一个整数，按照从小到大的顺序依次输出方程在$[1,m]$内的一个整数解。</p>\n"},{"title":"# 样例一","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n\n<h4>input</h4>\n<pre>2 10\n1\n-2\n1\n\n</pre>\n\n<h4>output</h4>\n<pre>1\n1\n\n</pre>\n\n"},{"title":"# 样例二","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n\n<h4>input</h4>\n<pre>2 10\n2\n-3\n1\n\n</pre>\n\n<h4>output</h4>\n<pre>2\n1\n2\n\n</pre>\n\n"},{"title":"# 样例三","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n\n<h4>input</h4>\n<pre>2 10\n1\n3\n2\n\n</pre>\n\n<h4>output</h4>\n<pre>0\n\n</pre>\n\n"},{"title":"# 限制与约定","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n\n<p>对于30%的数据，$0 &lt; n \\le 2$，$|a_i| \\le 100$，$a_n \\ne 0$，$m \\le 100$；</p>\n<p>对于50%的数据，$0 &lt; n \\le 100$，$|a_i| \\le 10^{100}$，$a_n \\ne 0$，$m \\le 100$；</p>\n<p>对于70%的数据，$0 &lt; n \\le 100$，$|a_i| \\le 10^{10000}$，$a_n \\ne 0$，$m \\le 10000$；</p>\n<p>对于100%的数据，$0 &lt; n \\le 100$，$|a_i| \\le 10^{10000}$，$a_n \\ne 0$，$m \\le 1000000$。</p>\n<p><strong>时间限制：</strong>$1\\texttt{s}$</p>\n<p><strong>内存限制：</strong>$128\\texttt{MB}$</p>\n"},{"title":"# 下载","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n\n<p><a href=\"/download.php?type=problem&amp;id=20\">样例数据下载</a></p>\n\n"}]}